*'Bunting'<ref>{{cite web|title=RHS Plant Selector - ''Aquilegia'' 'Bunting'|url=http://apps.rhs.org.uk/plantselector/plant?plantid=4971|accessdate=11 June 2013}}</ref> (Songbird series)
